keywords take
---
Syntax: take <item>
        take <item> <container>
        take all
        take all.<keyword>

Take is an alias for the GET command. It picks up an item from the room
floor or from an open container.

  take sword          -- Picks up a sword from the room.
  take all            -- Picks up everything in the room.
  take sword chest    -- Takes a sword from a chest.
  take all.iron       -- Takes all items whose name contains "iron".

Items taken from a room go directly into your inventory. If you do not
have enough carrying capacity the item cannot be picked up.

See also: get drop put inventory
